{"TopicId":138112,"ForumId":66,"TopicTitle":"Modding Monday: Mouse Aim Flight!","CreatedByName":"SQUAD","CreatedById":66485,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-25T20:01:09Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SQUAD","CreatedById":66485,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-25T20:01:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cfigure data-orig-width=\u0022480\u0022 data-orig-height=\u002292\u0022 class=\u0022tmblr-full\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://40.media.tumblr.com/ab8ca95fa6c767a94ca66db2600759c6/tumblr_inline_o67bfnbqKB1rr2wit_540.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022image\u0022 data-orig-width=\u0022480\u0022 data-orig-height=\u002292\u0022\u003E\u003C/figure\u003E\u003Cfigure class=\u0022tmblr-embed tmblr-full\u0022 data-provider=\u0022youtube\u0022 data-orig-width=\u0022540\u0022 data-orig-height=\u0022304\u0022 data-url=\u0022https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMLaBBmNGXyk\u0022\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022540\u0022 height=\u0022304\u0022 id=\u0022youtube_iframe\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/MLaBBmNGXyk?feature=oembed\u0026amp;enablejsapi=1\u0026amp;origin=https://safe.txmblr.com\u0026amp;wmode=opaque\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/figure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://goo.gl/KP9xHd\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMAF\u003C/a\u003E is a tool that allows you to pilot aircraft with the mouse created by tetryds and ferram4, with credits for BahamutoD. The goal of the mod is to have a control system that can pilot anything you create as well as possible, making it easier to fly stably at extremely high speeds and also allowing for aiming with precision, without having to worry about wobbliness or trim! #KSP\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Moose Rocket Science","CreatedById":159931,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-25T20:15:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst! I love this mod!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"teag2","CreatedById":119694,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-25T20:15:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNice! I just found this mod myself, actually.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sampa","CreatedById":130079,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-25T20:32:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nok, adding this to my list of necessary mods\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Raptor9","CreatedById":67915,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-25T20:40:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is awesome\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jedensuscg","CreatedById":76475,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-26T02:54:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was just googling for something like this earlier! \u00A0Was trying to fly an early career plane and it was just liquiding me off. \u00A0There used to be a mod that let you input an airspeed or altitude or AoA and it would try and fly it for you but it does not seem to have made it to 1.1 yet. So going to download this NOW!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I downloaded this mod and with it was able to \u00A0land a very early career aircraft consistently. \u00A0I had a quicksave of my plane in an unstable left base and time after time I could land without ripping off wheels or kerbal heads.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-27T06:31:47Z\u0022 title=\u002204/27/2016 06:31  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 27, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by jedensuscg\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"federicoaa","CreatedById":94879,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-26T03:24:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow different is this mod to Atmosphere autopilot?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/124417-11-atmosphereautopilot-152/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Best_JAxeel","CreatedById":162372,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-26T04:42:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYAY I can aim like in WT!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Morse","CreatedById":154930,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-26T07:18:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222540301\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022138112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461641043\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002294879\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022federicoaa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, federicoaa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow different is this mod to Atmosphere autopilot?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe author of MAF has already answered to that:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris implementation is much more complex, but\u00A0our mods have different purposes, and I agree, it\u0027s pretty awesome.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZentroCatson","CreatedById":143939,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-26T10:53:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCool! I\u0027ll definitely give it a try! But\u2026 the start of that music video made my ears bleed\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sealed:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_lipssealed.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sealed:\u0022\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-26T11:02:57Z\u0022 title=\u002204/26/2016 11:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 26, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by ZentroCatson\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E:V\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dreambish","CreatedById":140312,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-26T19:22:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGlorious! Now I don\u0027t have to contort my fingers to reach Q,E and WASD at the same time with only one hand!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe entire Dota community scorns me now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sanic","CreatedById":149920,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-26T20:52:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222540387\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022138112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221461645764\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162372\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Best_JAxeel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, Best_JAxeel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYAY I can aim like in WT!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKrussian bias\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Best_JAxeel","CreatedById":162372,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-27T06:35:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Top